üöÄ VendingManager: IoT Vending Machine Management System

VendingManager is a comprehensive Full-Stack system simulating the management of a network of intelligent vending machines (IoT). The project demonstrates a modern, distributed architecture combining a server-side rendered administrative panel (MVC), a public client application (SPA), and real-time communication.

The application is fully containerized using Docker & Docker Compose and deployed on Microsoft Azure cloud.

üåê Live Demo

The application is fully deployed and available online:

